name: 2017 Team Series: Event 7
description:
On a 20-minute clock, for max reps/pounds:
Partner 1:
  0:00-2:00 Handstand push-ups
  2:00-4:00 Rest
  4:00-6:00 Double-unders
  6:00-8:00 Rest
  8:00-10:00 1-rep-max back squat
Then, Partner 2:
  10:00-12:00 1-rep-max back squat
  12:00-14:00 Rest
  14:00-16:00 Double-unders
  16:00-18:00 Rest
  18:00-20:00 Handstand push-ups

Score is total reps from each component. For example, if Athlete 1 completes 40
handstand push-ups, 160 double-unders and a max squat of 350 lb., and Athlete 2 completes 35 handstand push-ups, 175 double-unders and a 250-lb. squat, the teamâ€™s score will be 1,010.
